git clone --branch nightly https://github.com/neovim/neovim.git
make -C neovim clean cmake nvim

### Expected behavior

no redefinition

### Neovim version (nvim -v)

5def8714ad70e71e07773960269fff5c0c95e7ab

### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?

no

no term

no term

### Installation

manual
